-Installation-
  Arduino
    http://arduino.cc

  MongoDB
    http://www.atinux.fr/2011/10/08/introduction-et-installation-de-mongodb/

  NodeJS
    http://nodejs.org/

  NodeJS libs
      keypad http://playground.arduino.cc/code/Keypad
      onewire http://playground.arduino.cc/Learning/OneWire
  git/github
    install git - http://git-scm.com/downloads
    create github account - http://github.com/
    open terminal and insert the following commands to copy the repo :
      -git clone https://github.com/ruyoliveira/BMS.git
      -cd BMS
      -git remote add upstream https://github.com/ruyoliveira/BMS.git
      -git fetch upstream
    ##Outros comandos
    
    *Criar um branch
      -git branch nome_do_branch
    *Usar o branch
      -git checkout nome_do_branch
    *Enviar alteracoes feitas ao repositorio(github)
      -git push origin nome_do_branch
